    <ul>
        <li>Provider: <span id="program_data_provider"></span></li>
        <li>Last update: <span id="program_data_last_update"></span></li>
        <li>Number of programs: <span id="program_data_num_programs"></span></li>
        <li>Program information till: <span id="program_data_info_till"></span></li>
